'''倫敦紹森德機場'''或'''紹森德機場'''（{{lang-en|'''London Southend Airport'''}}，{{Airport codes|SEN|EGMC}}）是坐落於[[雅息士郡|雅息士]][[羅奇福德區|羅奇福德區]]的[[國際機場|國際機場]]，距離[[查令十字|倫敦中心點]]約{{convert|42|mi|km}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.google.co.uk/maps/dir/Charing+Cross+Rd,+London,+UK/London+Southend+Airport,+Southend-on-Sea,+Essex+SS2+6YF,+United+Kingdom/|title=Google Maps|author=|date=|work=Google Maps|accessdate=2016-06-06|archive-date=2018-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181001161909/https://www.google.co.uk/maps/dir/Charing+Cross+Rd,+London,+UK/London+Southend+Airport,+Southend-on-Sea,+Essex+SS2+6YF,+United+Kingdom/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1960年代起，绍森德一直是[[英国|英国]]第三繁忙的机场<ref name=london110616>[http://www.londonnet.co.uk/news/2011/jun/easyjet-helps-make-southend-londons-sixth-major-airport.html EasyJet Helps Make Southend London's Sixth Major Airport] {{Wayback|url=http://www.londonnet.co.uk/news/2011/jun/easyjet-helps-make-southend-londons-sixth-major-airport.html |date=20110619045342 }} London.net, published 2011-06-16, accessed 2011-06-17</ref>，直直到1970年代末被[[伦敦斯坦斯特德机场|伦敦斯坦斯特德机场]]超过。<ref name=ft110616>[http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/61c726f6-97e5-11e0-85e9-00144feab49a.html EasyJet to offer flights from Southend] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/61c726f6-97e5-11e0-85e9-00144feab49a.html |date=20110619014416 }} [[金融時報|Financial Times]], published 2011-06-16, accessed 2011-06-17</ref>绍森德机场2008年被{{tsl|en|Stobart Group||Stobart Group}}收购，<ref name=ft110616/>发展计划也从那时开始，<ref>[http://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/3943522.Updated__Southend_Airport_sold_to_Eddie_Stobart/ Airport sold to Eddie Stobart] {{Wayback|url=http://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/3943522.Updated__Southend_Airport_sold_to_Eddie_Stobart/ |date=20111015192129 }} Echo, published 2008-12-03, accessed 2011-06-17</ref><ref name=bbc110404>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-essex-12957610 London Southend Airport's new control tower operational] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-essex-12957610 |date=20201123181504 }} [[英国广播公司|BBC]], published 2011-04-04, accessed 2011-06-17</ref><ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/essex/8576446.stm Minister gives Southend airport the go-ahead] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/essex/8576446.stm |date=20170828112136 }} [[英国广播公司|BBC]], published 2010-03-19, accessed 2011-06-17</ref>其中[[易捷航空|易捷航空]]计划从2012年4月开始运行定期航班并在绍森德机场开设基地。<ref>[http://corporate.easyjet.com/media/latest-news/news-year-2011/16-06-2011.aspx?sc_lang=en easyJet to launch services from London Southend Airport] {{Wayback|url=http://corporate.easyjet.com/media/latest-news/news-year-2011/16-06-2011.aspx?sc_lang=en |date=20140222064216 }} [[易捷航空|EasyJet]], accessed 2011-06-17</ref>營運者希望於2020年的使用量達至200萬人。<ref name=london110616 /><ref name=bbc110404 />

==位置==
伦敦绍森德机场位于[[羅奇福德|羅奇福德]]和[[滨海绍森德|滨海绍森德]] 之间，在伦敦以东[[埃塞克斯郡|埃塞克斯郡]]滨海绍森德以北{{Convert|1.5|NM|abbr=on|lk=in}}。<ref name="aip"/>从[[羅奇福德站|羅奇福德站]] (离机场3/4英里)到[[伦敦利物浦街车站|伦敦利物浦街车站]] 有频繁的火车，耗时50分钟。

新建的[[绍森德机场车站|绍森德机场车站]]2011年7月启用。<ref name=rail110617>[http://www.rail.co/2011/06/17/stobart-group-strikes-deal-with-easyjet-at-southend-airport/ Stobart Group strikes deal with easyJet at Southend Airport] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rail.co/2011/06/17/stobart-group-strikes-deal-with-easyjet-at-southend-airport/ |date=20120118150359 }} rail.co, published 2011-06-17, accessed 2011-06-17</ref>到[[斯特拉福德车站|斯特拉福德车站]]的直达列车耗时44分钟，是机场能够吸引[[2012年奥林匹克运动会|2012年奥林匹克运动会]]期间的游客.<ref name=rail110617 />

==设施==
机场[[航站楼|航站楼]]拥有咖啡厅、登記臺、候機室、租车柜台、照相亭、[[ATM|ATM]]（可取[[欧元|欧元]]和[[英镑|英镑]]）、消息旅游信息点、VIP休息厅和接待区。距离航站楼前100米的地方有出租车等候区和免费停车场，同時在機場與羅奇福德站之間還開有臨時穿梭巴士，以方便想前往[[中倫敦|中倫敦]]旅遊的旅客，當新的機場地鐵站建成後，穿梭巴士將停止運行。

